<Subtitle>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>1</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>10116</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>16632</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克沿着小路往前走。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>2</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>16632</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>22678</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他来到房子前，然后躲到了灌木丛后面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>3</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>22678</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>29697</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在等食人魔的妻子出来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>4</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>29697</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>37471</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>女人手里提着一个木桶。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>5</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>37471</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>41437</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“她要去井里提水了。”杰克心想。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>6</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>41437</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>49996</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他又等了一会儿。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>7</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>49997</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>55929</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“就是现在！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>8</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>55929</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>63745</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克偷偷跑了进去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>9</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>63746</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>66930</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>杰克看到了一个大盆。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>10</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>66930</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>71909</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>里面装满了脏衣服。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>11</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>71909</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>76515</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他快速躲到衣服下面。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>12</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>76515</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>81845</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>不久，巨大的脚步声响起。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>13</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>81845</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>90923</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>咚！咚！咚！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>14</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>90923</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>95408</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔突然吸了吸鼻子。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>15</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>95408</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>101297</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他在房间里闻来闻去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>16</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>101297</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>109142</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“Fee！Fi！Fo！Fum！”食人魔大喊，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>17</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>109142</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>115211</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到了一个英国男孩儿的味道！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>18</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>115211</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>128595</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔又吸了吸鼻子，继续闻来闻去。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>19</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>128595</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>132121</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的妻子从外面回来。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>20</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>132121</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>135892</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你在做什么？”她问。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>21</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>135892</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>141885</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到了那个男孩儿的味道！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>22</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>141885</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>149361</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>我要找到他！”食人魔大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>23</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>149361</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>152375</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔的妻子看着他。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>24</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>152375</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>157620</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“你闻到了那个男孩儿的味道吗？”她问，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>25</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>157621</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>161319</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“那个偷了你金子的男孩儿？”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>26</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>161319</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>165011</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“对！”食人魔大喊。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>27</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>165011</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>168747</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>他的眼里充满了愤怒。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>28</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>168747</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>173349</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他还偷了我的金母鸡！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>29</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>173349</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>182282</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我知道他在哪儿！”食人魔的妻子说。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>30</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>182282</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>187416</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>她跑到烤箱前面，打开了门。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>31</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>187416</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>192360</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>但杰克不在里面！</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>32</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>192360</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>198857</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>食人魔愤怒地跺了跺脚。</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>33</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>198857</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>206499</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“我闻到他的味道了！”食人魔说，</Text>
  </Paragraph>
  <Paragraph>
    <Number>34</Number>
    <StartMilliseconds>206499</StartMilliseconds>
    <EndMilliseconds>211662</EndMilliseconds>
    <Text>“他就在这里！”</Text>
  </Paragraph>
